      <title>大学在基础设施上投入巨资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/colleges-are-spending-big-on-infrastructure-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据穆迪评级公司的最新报告，该公司估计，未来十年学校需要 7500 亿至 9500 亿美元才能“在减少延期维护、升级设施和建设对战略定位至关重要的新项目方面取得重大进展”。丹妮尔·莫兰 (Danielle Moran) 在 8 月 23 日的“彭博收盘价”节目中讨论了高校的基础设施需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/colleges-are-spending-big-on-infrastructure-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:18:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚将在 120 天内签署埃克森美孚资产出售协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/nigeria-set-to-sign-off-on-exxon-asset-sale-within-120-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚监管机构表示，预计将在四个月内正式同意埃克森美孚公司将其石油和天然气资产出售给 Seplat Energy Plc，从而结束 2022 年 2 月首次宣布的交易停滞状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/nigeria-set-to-sign-off-on-exxon-asset-sale-within-120-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:06:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西破产潮来袭 债权人争夺土地举步维艰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/creditors-struggle-to-seize-land-in-brazil-as-bankruptcies-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊雨林城市锡诺普的一项法庭判决保护了一家玉米和大豆生产商的土地不被债权人没收，这一判决在法里亚利马大道（巴西版的华尔街）产生了反响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/creditors-struggle-to-seize-land-in-brazil-as-bankruptcies-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔宣布通胀问题取得胜利：PGIM 的柯林斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/powell-has-declared-victory-on-inflation-pgim-s-collins-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PGIM 固定收益执行投资组合顾问迈克尔·柯林斯 (Michael Collins) 表示，美联储应该立即开始降息，但会缓慢而有条不紊地采取行动。他在彭博电视台发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/powell-has-declared-victory-on-inflation-pgim-s-collins-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 13:35:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>施瓦布的桑德斯并不担心鲍威尔的政策转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/schwab-s-sonders-isn-t-worried-about-powell-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉信理财首席投资策略师 Liz Ann Sonders 表示，她并不担心美联储开始降息，但她表示，激进的降息周期可能会带来麻烦。她正在接受“彭博监测”节目采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/schwab-s-sonders-isn-t-worried-about-powell-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 13:25:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞拒绝左翼总理，法国等待马克龙人选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/le-pen-rejects-left-wing-premier-as-france-awaits-macron-s-pick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国极右翼国民联盟领导人玛丽娜·勒庞告诉埃马纽埃尔·马克龙，她的组织将反对来自左翼新人民阵线联盟的总理，因为总统正在寻求寻找一位能够在分裂议会的情况下执政的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/le-pen-rejects-left-wing-premier-as-france-awaits-macron-s-pick</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚反对派政府因银行纠纷停止石油生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/libyan-rival-government-to-stop-oil-output-amid-central-bank-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚东部政府表示，将停止原油生产和出口，因为其与位于的黎波里的对手争夺央行和国家石油资源，有可能引发新一轮冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/libyan-rival-government-to-stop-oil-output-amid-central-bank-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔与科威特签署新的长期液化天然气供应协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/qatar-set-to-sign-new-15-year-lng-supply-deal-with-kuwait</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔与科威特签署了一项为期 15 年的新液化天然气供应协议，这是第二份供应合同，这将有助于缓解今年夏天已被迫减产的发电厂的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/qatar-set-to-sign-new-15-year-lng-supply-deal-with-kuwait</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 06:49:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔转变立场、ETF 资金流入推动比特币逼近 65,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/bitcoin-btc-flirts-with-65-000-on-powell-pivot-streak-of-etf-flows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有迹象表明美联储将放松货币政策的情况下，受美国专用交易所交易基金需求复苏的推动，比特币约三周来首次触及 65,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/bitcoin-btc-flirts-with-65-000-on-powell-pivot-streak-of-etf-flows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 05:56:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街因美联储押注而重振大宗小宗交易：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/asian-stocks-eye-fed-bounce-after-powell-speech-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储降息的前景再次引发人们对牛市将从飞速发展的科技领域中拓展的猜测，股市徘徊在历史高位附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/asian-stocks-eye-fed-bounce-after-powell-speech-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 22:33:42 GMT</pubDate>
